    &CELL
      ABC 6.0 6.0 6.0
    &END CELL
    &COORD
      Ar     0.100000  0.120000  0.110000
    &END COORD
    &KIND Ar
      BASIS_SET DZVP-GTH-PADE
      POTENTIAL GTH-PADE-q8
    &END KIND
